{"tid":1725703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不分化不割𥱊並唔係咁用","createTime":"2019-11-15T23:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T00:02:48.000Z","uid":292717,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3fbeba098c0bb1919099f3e1ecd2d1c5ac49d623","tid":1725703,"uid":292717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T23:52:38.000Z","msg":"今日風向又去返和理非勇武割唔割<br />\n全日Facebook俾轉載不割𥱊洗版，宜家究竟係和理非想割定係前線驚被割？？<br />\n前線都開始分兩種，你叫和理非點適應呢？<br />\n火魔法攻舖仲要樓上係住宅你想要和理非點接受先？<br />\n中大理工打到阿富汗咁，你班和理非喺屋企睇直播唔幫拖仲要𠲖𠲖哦哦，前線又仲可以點呢？<br />\n不割𥱊係比前缐推動力唔係縱容，我地同班狗唔同，佢哋殺人放火姦淫擄掠打家劫舍，我地只係想光復香港清算狗賊，係要將香港重光唔係淪陷呀<br />\n同路人們，大家瞄準啲，有氣有力嘅仲有大把地方用得著<br />\n721黑狗唔捉嘅鄉黑，我哋去探下佢哋囉，車房白頭佬、小牛農莊⋯⋯大把嘢未做<br />\n831班狗咁高興，好多狗仔狗女都想一齊試吓架<br />\nDC佬撞完人仲風流快活緊喎<br />\n福建佬仲日日喺同鄉會打緊麻雀<br />\n建制班冚家鏟點計都西撚過翠X莎X啩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瞄準D啦，射得中的話，莫講話和理非，中立淺藍都實轉會，我地要贏仲要贏就一齊贏<br />\n<br />\n瞄準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瞄準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瞄準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2e2b8bcb0cfb07ad4c62a5ae6fe10697e4f94e","tid":1725703,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T23:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bfd00c862cc8146831fd2b208a624d586ab582","tid":1725703,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T23:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" 